data.description: Absolutely stunning home that backs up to Hole 15 at the Golf Club at Champions Circle, what more could you ask for! This 4 bed 3 bath home shows like a model home, and has been upgraded with great finishes and well cared for by loving owners. Plantation shutters, newer flooring, interior and exterior freshly painted, upgraded light fixtures, newer HVAC both upstairs and down with transferable warranty and newer roof but the extended patio is the true must see! Livingroom boast high ceilings and so many windows bringing in all the natural light.  All stainless steel appliances in the kitchen, and with so many cabinets as well as the butler's pantry, you will never run out of storage space. The beautifully appointed primary bedroom has a luxurious on-suite and custom closet that anyone would envy!  Upstairs boast  another living space and 3 bedrooms.  The backyard is a true oasis with an amazing covered patio that overlooks the pristine golf course.  Check out the 3D Virtual Floor Plan!
